# <Icon icon="mdi:book-open-page-variant" class="inline-block" /> Documentation

Welcome to the documentation! This page is written in **Markdown** and rendered using [mdsvex](https://mdsvex.com/).

## What is mdsvex?

MDsveX is a markdown preprocessor for Svelte. It allows you to:

- Write content in Markdown
- Use Svelte components inside your markdown
- Add interactivity to your docs

## Interactive Example

Here's a counter component embedded right in this markdown file:

<div class="not-prose my-6">
  <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
    <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
      <h2 class="card-title">Interactive Counter</h2>
      <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary">{count}</p>
      <div class="card-actions">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick={() => count++}>
          Increment
        </button>
        <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick={() => count--}>
          Decrement
        </button>
        <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick={() => count = 0}>
          Reset
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

